# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:11
translate french jamie0_86844818:

    # "I decide to go see Jamie. I walk up to her door and knock twice."
    "Je décide d’aller voir Jamie. Je m’approche de sa porte et frappe deux fois."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:15
translate french jamie0_6d10994a:

    # "After a minute or so, she answers, wearing cloth shorts and a t-shirt tight enough that I can make out the outlines of her nipples through it."
    "Au bout d’une minute environ, elle ouvre, vêtue d’un short en tissu et d’un t-shirt assez moulant pour que je puisse distinguer le contour de ses tétons à travers."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:17
translate french jamie0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_004.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_004.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:18
translate french jamie0_ae29242d:

    # gnd "Oh hi, [pcname]. What's up?"
    gnd "Oh salut, [pcname]. Quoi de neuf ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:21
translate french jamie0_1142edfa:

    # pc "I was just wondering what you were up to."
    pc "Je me demandais juste ce que tu faisais."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:23
translate french jamie0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_005.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_005.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:24
translate french jamie0_5c68d96a:

    # gnd "I'm just watching TV. Want to come inside and hang out?"
    gnd "Je regarde la télé. Tu veux entrer pour traîner un peu ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:27
translate french jamie0_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:30
translate french jamie0_8530d6f7:

    # pc "Not right now."
    pc "Pas tout de suite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:35
translate french jamie0_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:36
translate french jamie0_7761ed77:

    # gnd "I'm sorry, I'm not really feeling up to going anywhere tonight."
    gnd "Désolée, je ne me sens pas vraiment d'humeur à sortir ce soir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:37
translate french jamie0_e3b9539d:

    # gnd "I'm in the middle of a TV show and already dressed for bed."
    gnd "Je suis en plein milieu d'une série et je suis déjà en pyjama."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:39
translate french jamie0_9c09b9dd:

    # gnd "Do you want to come inside and chat a bit though?"
    gnd "Tu veux quand même entrer pour discuter un peu ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:47
translate french jamie0_4f724fa8:

    # gnd "What?"
    gnd "Quoi ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:48
translate french jamie0_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "À plus."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:49
translate french jamie0_2c2201d1:

    # gnd "Uh okay, see you later then."
    gnd "Euh, d'accord, à plus tard alors."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:51
translate french jamie0_74706d57:

    # "She looks disappointed as she shuts the door and I walk back over to my house."
    "Elle a l'air déçue en fermant la porte et je retourne chez moi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:56
translate french leavejamie_fc2cf32e:

    # gnd "Okay, maybe we can do something some other time?"
    gnd "Bon, on pourra peut-être faire quelque chose une autre fois ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:57
translate french leavejamie_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:58
translate french leavejamie_60ba3b2f:

    # gnd "Well, I'll see you later then."
    gnd "Bon, à plus tard alors."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:59
translate french leavejamie_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "À plus."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:60
translate french leavejamie_74706d57:

    # "She looks disappointed as she shuts the door and I walk back over to my house."
    "Elle a l’air déçue en fermant la porte et je retourne chez moi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:68
translate french tvchatwithjamie_b827e096:

    # "She leads me to the living room, where the TV is paused on a show that I don't recognize."
    "Elle m’emmène dans le salon, où la télé est en pause sur une série que je ne reconnais pas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:69
translate french tvchatwithjamie_1410557b:

    # gnd "I was just trying to finish up this series that I've been watching before school starts up again."
    gnd "J’essayais juste de finir cette série que je regarde avant la rentrée."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:70
translate french tvchatwithjamie_442eef5c:

    # pc "Cool. I barely watch any TV anymore."
    pc "Cool. Je ne regarde presque plus la télé."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:71
translate french tvchatwithjamie_e0203869:

    # gnd "Really? I love TV. I probably watch too much."
    gnd "Vraiment ? J'adore la télé. J'en regarde probablement trop."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:73
translate french tvchatwithjamie_5407ea16:

    # "We sit there for a few moments in an awkward silence. There are a couple times when Jamie seems like she wants to say something, but doesn't."
    "On reste assis là quelques instants dans un silence gênant. À plusieurs reprises, Jamie semble vouloir dire quelque chose, mais elle ne le fait pas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:74
translate french tvchatwithjamie_58b01cd5:

    # "It feels very strange, like she is uncomfortable with me for some reason. Like there is something between us."
    "C'est très étrange, comme si elle se sentait mal à l'aise avec moi pour une raison quelconque. Comme s'il y avait quelque chose entre nous."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:75
translate french tvchatwithjamie_396a0d53:

    # "I have to break this silence with literally any conversation."
    "Je dois briser ce silence en engageant n'importe quelle conversation."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:76
translate french tvchatwithjamie_1171aaad:

    # pc "Oh, I have a cell phone now."
    pc "Oh, j'ai un portable maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:78
translate french tvchatwithjamie_5c1dfc7a:

    # gnd "Awesome, what's your number?"
    gnd "Super, c'est quoi ton numéro ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:79
translate french tvchatwithjamie_53b692f6:

    # "I tell her my new phone number and she puts it into her phone."
    "Je lui donne mon nouveau numéro et elle l'enregistre dans son téléphone."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:81
translate french tvchatwithjamie_b9feb81a:

    # "Then she turns her phone around and holds it up to take a picture of herself."
    "Puis elle retourne son téléphone et le tient devant elle pour se prendre en photo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:83
translate french tvchatwithjamie_5ad0b0e8:

    # gnd "I sent you a text message, along with a picture of me so you can add me into your contacts, and we can chat whenever."
    gnd "Je t'ai envoyé un SMS avec une photo de moi pour que tu puisses m'ajouter à tes contacts, et qu'on puisse discuter quand tu veux."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:88
translate french tvchatwithjamie_ea0a9e4e:

    # pc "I got it. I'll just add you to my contacts real quick."
    pc "Je l'ai reçu. Je vais juste t'ajouter à mes contacts rapidement."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:89
translate french tvchatwithjamie_d7eecc80:

    # pc "And done."
    pc "Et voilà."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:90
translate french tvchatwithjamie_7a48c010:

    # gnd "Awesome."
    gnd "Génial."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:93
translate french tvchatwithjamie_a06bb2fa:

    # pc "Great. I'll be sure to add you as soon as I get back home and get the phone set up."
    pc "Super. Je t'ajouterai dès que je serai rentrée chez moi et que j'aurai configuré mon téléphone."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:95
translate french tvchatwithjamie_570f0e90:

    # "She sits on the couch next to me, leaning back against the arm rest to face me, her bare legs folded underneath her."
    "Elle s'assoit sur le canapé à côté de moi, se calant contre l'accoudoir pour me faire face, les jambes nues repliées sous elle."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:96
translate french tvchatwithjamie_06525d7f:

    # gnd "Do you want to watch my TV show with me?"
    gnd "Tu veux regarder ma série avec moi ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:97
translate french tvchatwithjamie_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:98
translate french tvchatwithjamie_49f2ae65:

    # gnd "It's called The Nieces of Callahan. Have you ever watched any of it?"
    gnd "Elle s’appelle The Nieces of Callahan. Tu en as déjà vu un épisode ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:99
translate french tvchatwithjamie_c7fa5d68:

    # pc "Nope."
    pc "Non."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:100
translate french tvchatwithjamie_f8a2b09a:

    # gnd "Well I'm sure you'll be completely lost, but I'll try to catch you up."
    gnd "Bon, je suis sûre que tu vas être complètement perdu, mais je vais essayer de te mettre au courant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:102
translate french tvchatwithjamie_fb6f3632:

    # "She plays the show, but talks pretty much the whole time through it, explaining which character was which, who was sleeping with who, and which characters she liked and hated."
    "Elle lance la série, mais parle pratiquement tout le temps pendant qu’elle passe, expliquant quel personnage était qui, qui couchait avec qui, et quels personnages elle aimait et détestait."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:103
translate french tvchatwithjamie_8a51ccf8:

    # "The show doesn't interest me too much, but as we sit together, she moves closer and closer, until our sides are touching."
    "La série ne m’intéresse pas trop, mais alors que nous sommes assis ensemble, elle se rapproche de plus en plus, jusqu’à ce que nos côtés se touchent."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:104
translate french tvchatwithjamie_df180490:

    # "I think about putting an arm around her shoulder, but I'm not sure what she would think about it."
    "Je pense à passer un bras autour de ses épaules, mais je ne sais pas trop ce qu’elle en penserait."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:105
translate french tvchatwithjamie_02a91ff8:

    # "Still, being there next to her is nice."
    "Mais bon, c’est agréable d’être là à côté d’elle."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:106
translate french tvchatwithjamie_7c085331:

    # "Finally, the show ends."
    "Finalement, la série se termine."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:108
translate french tvchatwithjamie_616bf526:

    # gnd "Did you like it?"
    gnd "Tu as aimé ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:109
translate french tvchatwithjamie_28b82c1c:

    # pc "Honestly, I couldn't really follow it, but what I saw was okay."
    pc "Honnêtement, je n’ai pas vraiment suivi, mais ce que j’ai vu était pas mal."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:110
translate french tvchatwithjamie_82d9fc6f:

    # gnd "Yeah, you kind of have to watch it from the beginning."
    gnd "Ouais, il faut en quelque sorte le regarder depuis le début."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:111
translate french tvchatwithjamie_95fb6df8:

    # gnd "Thanks for sitting through it with me anyways. That was nice."
    gnd "Merci quand même de l’avoir regardé avec moi. C’était sympa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:112
translate french tvchatwithjamie_4eb9bd3a:

    # pc "Yeah it was. I enjoyed it."
    pc "Ouais, c’était sympa. J’ai bien aimé."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:115
translate french tvchatwithjamie_0bde0b2d:

    # gnd "I'm so glad you're back in town. I know we didn't hang out much before you left, but I've always liked you and thought about you."
    gnd "Je suis tellement contente que tu sois de retour en ville. Je sais qu’on ne traînait pas beaucoup ensemble avant ton départ, mais je t’ai toujours apprécié et j’ai toujours pensé à toi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:116
translate french tvchatwithjamie_48b6a79b:

    # pc "Yeah, we had some good times when we were younger."
    pc "Ouais, on a passé de bons moments quand on était plus jeunes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:117
translate french tvchatwithjamie_234edbbb:

    # gnd "Yeah we did. I wish we would have stayed friends through high school. I made a lot of bad decisions then."
    gnd "Oui, c'est vrai. J'aurais aimé qu'on reste amis pendant le lycée. J'ai pris beaucoup de mauvaises décisions à l'époque."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:118
translate french tvchatwithjamie_ce0b88b7:

    # pc "I think we all did."
    pc "Je crois qu'on en a tous pris."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:119
translate french tvchatwithjamie_ec3ba06e:

    # gnd "Ain't that the truth."
    gnd "C'est bien vrai."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:121
translate french tvchatwithjamie_68579f4f:

    # "She smiles at me, and we stand awkwardly for a few moments."
    "Elle me sourit, et on reste là, un peu mal à l'aise, pendant quelques instants."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:122
translate french tvchatwithjamie_5a0cac5d:

    # pc "Anyways, I better get home."
    pc "Bref, je ferais mieux de rentrer chez moi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:124
translate french tvchatwithjamie_792d2ec7:

    # gnd "Okay, well thanks for coming to see me. Stop by anytime or send me a text if you want to chat."
    gnd "D'accord, eh bien merci d'être venue me voir. Passe quand tu veux ou envoie-moi un SMS si tu veux discuter."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:126
translate french tvchatwithjamie_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_007.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_007.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:127
translate french tvchatwithjamie_598f8960:

    # gnd "See you later."
    gnd "À plus tard."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:129
translate french tvchatwithjamie_3608be46:

    # "She smiles and waves as I walk out the door, shutting it behind me, and walk over to my house."
    "Elle me sourit et me fait signe de la main tandis que je sors, refermant la porte derrière moi, et que je me dirige vers chez moi."

